**[低] 性能问题：硬编码列名和缺乏错误处理**
`columns` 列表被硬编码为 `"id", "name", "value", "timestamp"`，如果表结构变化，代码需要手动更新，增加了维护成本。此外，代码缺乏对数据库连接失败、查询超时或数据不一致的异常处理，可能引发同步中断或数据丢失。

### 改进代码
```java
import java.util.*;
import java.sql.*;

public class FullDataSync {
    private Connection sourceConn;
    private Connection targetConn;
    private String sourceTable;
    private String targetTable;
    private int batchSize = 1000;
    private int pageSize = 10000;
    private List<String> columns;

    public FullDataSync(Connection sourceConn, Connection targetConn, String sourceTable, String targetTable) throws SQLException {
        this.sourceConn = sourceConn;
        this.targetConn = targetConn;
        this.sourceTable = sourceTable;
        this.targetTable = targetTable;
        this.columns = fetchColumns(sourceConn, sourceTable);
    }

    private List<String> fetchColumns(Connection conn, String table) throws SQLException {
        List<String> cols = new ArrayList<>();
        DatabaseMetaData meta = conn.getMetaData();
        ResultSet rs = meta.getColumns(null, null, table, null);
        while (rs.next()) {
            cols.add(rs.getString("COLUMN_NAME"));
        }
        rs.close();
        return cols;
    }

    public void syncAllData() throws SQLException {
        targetConn.setAutoCommit(false);
        int offset = 0;
        while (true) {
            String selectQuery = "SELECT * FROM " + sourceTable + " LIMIT " + pageSize + " OFFSET " + offset;
            Statement stmt = sourceConn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs = stmt.executeQuery(selectQuery);

            String placeholders = String.join(", ", Collections.nCopies(columns.size(), "?"));
            String insertQuery = "INSERT INTO " + targetTable + " (" + String.join(", ", columns) + ") VALUES (" + placeholders + ")";
            PreparedStatement pstmt = targetConn.prepareStatement(insertQuery);

            int count = 0;
            while (rs.next()) {
                for (int i = 0; i < columns.size(); i++) {
                    pstmt.setObject(i + 1, rs.getObject(columns.get(i)));
                }
                pstmt.addBatch();
                count++;

                if (count % batchSize == 0) {
                    pstmt.executeBatch();
                }
            }

            if (count > 0 && count % batchSize != 0) {
                pstmt.executeBatch();
            }

            targetConn.commit();
            rs.close();
            stmt.close();
            pstmt.close();

            if (count < pageSize) {
                break;
            }
            offset += pageSize;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        try {
            Connection source = DriverManager.getConnection("jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/source_db", "user", "pass");
            Connection target = DriverManager.getConnection("jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/target_db", "user", "pass");
            FullDataSync sync = new FullDataSync(source, target, "source_data", "target_data");
            sync.syncAllData();
            source.close();
            target.close();
        } catch (SQLException e) {
            System.err.println("同步失败: " + e.getMessage());
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}
```

### 最佳实践
1. 在全量数据同步中，使用分页查询（如 `LIMIT` 和 `OFFSET`）分批加载数据，避免一次性加载大量数据到内存，防止内存溢出并提高性能。
2. 优化事务管理：在同步开始时禁用自动提交，使用批处理执行插入，并在每页数据同步完成后提交一次事务，减少数据库开销并确保数据一致性。

